<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-431] NPE in CBayesThetaNormalizerReducer when using HBase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-431</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m trying to use the complementary Bayes classifier and store the model in HBase (using BayesParameters.set(&quot;dataSource&quot;, &quot;hbase&quot;)).  When I run the MR jobs using CBayesDrvier, I get a NullPointerException in CBayesThetaNormalizerReducer at line 92:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;hBconf.set(new HBaseConfiguration(job));&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&apos;hBconf&apos; is a ThreadLocal&amp;lt;HBaseConfiguration&amp;gt; field and it looks like it has not been initialized.  I initialized it and the model built successfully.  I observed the same bug in the 0.3 release and in 0.4-SNAPSHOT.  I&apos;ll attach a patch that initializes the field.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
